description:
Add the NOTE_* syscall constants on Darwin, for use with kqueue:
http://developer.apple.com/library/mac/#documentation/Darwin/Reference/ManPages/man2/kqueue.2.html
./all.bash passes, and I re-generated zerrors for darwin using the command that they gave at the top.
